# Satellite repo/worktree mirroring rules
# Scopes the source behind `grove satellite repos push/pull` and
# `grove satellite worktree push/pull`: the delta/bundle/ship engines, the
# shared mirror machinery and pinned ssh/scp transport, the registry state
# file, the VM-side worktree-path plumbing verb, and the satellite E2E
# harness itself (endpoint seam, SSH simulator, real-VM provider, scenarios).
# Changes here should trigger the satellite-* E2E scenarios.

